MAIN GUIDE - https://emanual.robotis.com/docs/en/platform/turtlebot3/appendix_lds_01/#user-guide-for-gui

Libraries/downloads:

GCC - https://solarianprogrammer.com/2017/12/08/raspberry-pi-raspbian-install-gcc-compile-cpp-17-programs/
Boost - $ sudo apt-get install libboost-dev libboost-all-dev
LDS-01 driver - $ git clone https://github.com/ROBOTIS-GIT/hls_lfcd_lds_driver.git
QTcreator - https://www.engineersgarage.com/how-to-install-qt-in-raspberry-pi-part-29-38/

Directory for most things: $ cd hls_lfcd_lds_driver/applications/

How to see raw data:

$ cd hls_lfcd_lds_driver/applications/lds_driver/
$ ./lds_driver

(Make it stop by pressing ctrl+c)
